{"about_the_game":"<br><br><strong>The prologue will be a small slice of the full game</strong><br><br>Crystal guardians is a rogue-like tower defense game where you need to defend your base crystal on an expanding procedural generated battlefield. Gain a strategic advantage using the many towers + crystal combinations and unique item combinations stored in those towers. Make use of the expanding battlefield by placing towers on strategic position for maximal damage to the enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features of the prologue</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Enjoy the first 40 waves in the prologue version<br></li><li> Procedural generated levels, every run is different <br></li><li> Upgrade towers using items<br></li><li> Currently over 50 items available<br></li><li> 25 tower combinations<br></li><li> Extensive meta progression<br></li><li> Loads of different enemies</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Procedural expansion</h2><br>Keep expanding the battlefield while fighting off relentless waves of enemies. Use the newly gained grounds to gain an advantage on the enemies or find the lands secrets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744890/extras/progression-showcase-final-optimized.gif?t=1705875054\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A roguelike system</h2><br>Buy and use items on your towers to create the optimal strategy for you. With currently over 50 items to choose from.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744890/extras/roguelike-showcase-final-optimized.gif?t=1705875054\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Bosses</h2><br>Adapt your strategy to the unique boss waves<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744890/extras/boss-showcase-final-optimized.gif?t=1705875054\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Defeat Gilbert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/